<H3><A NAME="SEC154" HREF="bdg_toc.html#SEC154">Hong Kong</A></H3>
<B>nok.lcs.mit.edu</B>
GIF pictures of Hong Kong pop stars, buildings
and vistas are available in the <TT>`pub/hongkong/HKPA'</TT> directory.
<A NAME="IDX378"></A>
<A NAME="IDX379"></A>
6 p.m. - 6 a.m.
<P>
<P>Go to the <A HREF="bdg_150.html">previous</A>, <A HREF="bdg_152.html">next</A> section.<P>
