<H3><A NAME="SEC157" HREF="bdg_toc.html#SEC157">Libraries</A></H3>
<B>ftp.unt.edu</B>
The library directory contains numerous lists of
libraries with computerized card catalogs accessible through the Net.
<P>
<P>Go to the <A HREF="bdg_153.html">previous</A>, <A HREF="bdg_155.html">next</A> section.<P>
