<TITLE>Big Dummy's Guide to the Internet - Pictures</TITLE>
<P>Go to the <A HREF="bdg_161.html">previous</A>, <A HREF="bdg_163.html">next</A> section.<P>
<A NAME="IDX403"></A>
<H3><A NAME="SEC165" HREF="bdg_toc.html#SEC165">Pictures</A></H3>
