<TITLE>Big Dummy's Guide to the Internet - Gopher Agriculture</TITLE>
<P>Go to the <A HREF="bdg_184.html">previous</A>, <A HREF="bdg_186.html">next</A> section.<P>
<H3><A NAME="SEC188" HREF="bdg_toc.html#SEC188">Agriculture</A></H3>
<B>cyfer.esusda.gov</B>
More agricultural statistics and
regulations than most people will
ever need.
 
<B>usda.mannlib.cornell.edu</B>
More than 140 different types of 
agricultural data, most in Lotus 1-2-3
spreadsheet format.
<P>
