<H2><A NAME="SEC297" HREF="bdg_toc.html#SEC297">Mega Smileys</A></H2>
<P>
<B><CODE>C=}&#62;;*{))</CODE></B>
A drunk, devilish chef with a toupee in an updraft, a mustache, and
a double chin.
<P>
<B><CODE>}:^#})</CODE></B>
Updrafted bushy-mustached pointy nosed smiley with a double-chin.
