<H1><A NAME="SEC310" HREF="bdg_toc.html#SEC310">Internet Sites</A></H1>
<IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM SRC=logos/bdgtti.gif>
The following sites can be reached using <B>Telnet</B>.
See section <A HREF="bdg_89.html#SEC92">Telnet (Mining the Net, part I)</A> for an introduction to this service.
The general syntax is: <SAMP>`telnet &#60;site&#62; [port#]'</SAMP>.
