<hr>
<h1>Welcome Internaut!</h1>
You've made it to the Information Trap!
<p>
The Black Hole where everything gets Sucked In!
<p>
There is No Way Out of here!
<p>
This truly is the <b><a href="./this.html">End of the Internet!</a></b>
<p>
You can try to get Down to <a href="http://www.earth.com/Canada/Ontario/Sudbury/">Earth</a>, but you might as well stay at the <a href="http://www.moon.com/Apollo13/">Dark Side of the Moon</a>.
<br>
Or have a bite at the <a href="http://www.galaxy.com/">End of the Galaxy</a>. I know a little restaurant there, but that's another story...
<p>
While you're there, you might as well send <a href="mailto:foo@wrong.planet">me</a> a post-card!
<pre>








</pre>
