<hr>
<H1>Remote Sensing related equipment</H1>


<h2>Spectrometers</h2>
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.asdi.com/asd">ASD, Analytical Spectral Devices Inc.</A>
</UL>

<h3>Spectroscopy</h3>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.asdi.com/asd/other_sites.html">ASD's collection of Spectroscopy Related Sites</a>
<li><a href="http://www.techexpo.com/WWW/opto-knowledge/">The "Hyperspectrum" newsletter</a>, from Opto-Knowledge Systems, Inc. (OKSI)
</ul>

<h2>Small Satellites</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.newspace.com/Industry/AeroAstro/bitsy.html">Bitsy</a>, AeroAstro's micro satellite for remote sensing applications.
<li><a href="http://www.ee.surrey.ac.uk/EE/CSER/UOSAT/IJSSE/ijsse.html">The International Journal of Small Satellite Engineering</a>
<li><a href="http://www.ee.surrey.ac.uk/EE/CSER/UOSAT/SSHP/sshp.html">Small Satellite Home Page</a>
<li><a href="http://crsphome.ssc.nasa.gov/ssti/welcome.htm">NASA Small Spacecraft Technology Initiative Home Page</a>
</ul>

<h2>Global Positioning System</h2>
<ul>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.utexas.edu/depts/grg/gcraft/notes/gps/gps.html">The Global Positioning System (GPS)</A>
<li><a href="http://www.ggrweb.com/">GeoWeb company</a>
<li><a href="http://galaxy.einet.net/editors/john-beadles/introgps.htm">Introduction to GPS Applications</a>
<li><a href="http://www.he.net/~jbeadles/gps/index.htm">GPS Apps Archive</a>
<li><a href="http://www.he.net/~redsword/gps/market.htm">GPS Marketplace</a>
<li><a href="http://www.zilker.net/~hal/geoscience/gps.html">GPS</a>
<li><a href="ftp://sundae.triumf.ca/pub/peter/gpsfaq.txt">GPS FAQ, Peter Bennett</a>
<li><a href="http://www.dgps.com/">Differential Corrections Inc., Differential GPS and Traffic Messaging Services</a>
<li><a href="ftp://sundae.triumf.ca/pub/peter/index.html">NMEA-0183</a>
is a standard developed by the National Marine
Electronics Association for data communications between marine
instruments.
</ul>


<h2>Miscellaneous</h2>
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.vision1.com/">Resources for Vision and Imaging Professionals</a>
</ul>

