<HEAD><TITLE>The NOAA Satellites</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<pre><img src="logo/itc.gif" alt="ITC">            <img src="image/noaa.gif" alt="">           <img src="logo/sealwhb.gif" alt="WHB"></pre>
<hr>
<H1>The NOAA Satellites</H1>

First of all: a lot of general information about Satellite Imagery can be found in the following documents:
<br>
<a href="http://clever.net/webthing/people/nick/satfaq.html">Satellite Imagery FAQ</a>
<br>
<a href="http://www.geog.nottingham.ac.uk/remote/satfaq.html">The Satellite Imagery FAQ</a>
<br>
This document is available (with integrated bulletin board facility)
in the Remote Sensing InterFAQ at
<a href="http://clever.net/webthing/RS">Interactive version of the SatFAQ</a>
<p>
<h2><a href="image/noaa11.gif">Image of NOAA 11</a></h2>

<h2>NOAA Organization</h2>
<ul>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.noaa.gov/">NOAA Home page</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.esdim.noaa.gov/">NOAA ESDIM, Environmental Information Services</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.esdim.noaa.gov/NOAA-Catalog/">NOAA data set catalog</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.saa.noaa.gov/">SAA, Satellite Active Archive</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://sdsdabmc.nesdis.noaa.gov/">NCDC Satellite Services Branch</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://pegasus.nesdis.noaa.gov/pathfinder.html">Pathfinder program</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://sst-www.jpl.nasa.gov/">NOAA/NASA AVHRR Oceans Pathfinder Home Page</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://web.ngdc.noaa.gov/ngdc.html">NGDC, National Geophysical Data Center</A>
<LI><A HREF="gopher://esdim1.nodc.noaa.gov/">NOAA ESDIM, Directory Services Gopher</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/noaa/graph.html">NOAA, Interactive Organizational Chart</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.esdim.noaa.gov/">NOAA ESDIM</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://ns.noaa.gov/NESDIS/NESDIS_Home.html">NOAA NESDIS, National Environmental Satellite, Data, and Information Service</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://psbsgi1.fb4.noaa.gov:8080/MOSDEV.html">NOAA.SIS</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://psbsgi1.nesdis.noaa.gov:8080/EBB/ml/nic00.html">NOAA NOAA Satellite Services Division, <b>NOAA.SIS!</b></A>
<LI><A HREF="http://140.90.207.25:8080/EBB/ml/nic00.html">NOAA NOAA Satellite Services Division, <b>NOAA.SIS!</b></A>
<LI><A HREF="http://xtreme.gsfc.nasa.gov/">AVHRR Pathfinder Home Page</A>
<li><a href="http://orbit-net.nesdis.noaa.gov/orahome/">Office of Research and Applications</a>
</ul>

<h2>NOAA Polar Orbiter Data (POD) User's Guides</h2>
<ul>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.saa.noaa.gov:5726/pod_documents/">NOAA Polar Orbiter Data User's Guide (SAA)</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://sdsdabmc.nesdis.noaa.gov/POD/">NOAA Polar Orbiter Data User's Guide (NESDIS)</A>
