<p>
<LI><A HREF="file://ftp2.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/doc/noaaklm/">NOAA-K Draft Level 1b format documentation</A>
<li><a href="http://psbsgi1.nesdis.noaa.gov:8080/EBB/ml/nic121.html">NOAA Satellite Information, NOAA-K: a brief overview of changes</a>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.ccrs.nrcan.gc.ca/gcnet/guides/avhrr/avhrr.html">CCRS, NOAA AVHRR Data User's Guide</A>
