</ul>

<h2>SST, Sea Surface Temperature</h2>
<ul>
<LI><A HREF="http://geochange.er.usgs.gov/pub/magsst/magsst.html">Modern Average Global Sea-Surface Temperature</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://sst-www.jpl.nasa.gov/">NOAA/NASA AVHRR Oceans Pathfinder Home Page</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://podaac-www.jpl.nasa.gov/">PODAAC's NOAA/NASA AVHRR Oceans Pathfinder Home Page</A>
