<LI><A HREF="http://ssec.ssec.wisc.edu/data/">SSEC Real Time Data</A>
<li><a href="ftp://fermi.jhuapl.edu/www/seaspace/primer/primer_html.html">Primer on the Estimation of Sea Surface Temperature</a>
<br>Using Terascan Processing of NOAA AVHRR Satellite Data.
<li><a href="http://dcz.gso.uri.edu/avhrr-archive/archive.html">Sea Surface Temperature Satellite Images, at the University of Rhode Island</a>
