<LI><A HREF="http://www.sat.dundee.ac.uk/">NERC Satellite Station, Dundee</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://satftp.soest.hawaii.edu">Satellite Oceanography Laboratory, Hawaii</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.satlab.hawaii.edu">Satellite Oceanography Laboratory, SOEST, Hawaii</A>
<li> <a href="http://edcwww.cr.usgs.gov/glis/glis.html">USGS, EROS Data Center (EDC), GLIS (Global Land Information System)</a>
<LI><A HREF="http://edcwww.cr.usgs.gov/webglis">WEBGLIS</A>
<li><a href="http://sun1.cr.usgs.gov/glis/hyper/guide/">GLIS Guide</a>
<li><a href="http://www.eurimage.it/">Eurimage</a>
<li><a href="http://psc.apl.washington.edu/avhrr/AVHRRdatasites.html">AVHRR Data Sites</a>
<li><a href="http://www.dfd.dlr.de/ISIS/index.html">DLR, DFD - ISIS, Catalogue Overview</a>
<li><a href="http://www.dfd.dlr.de/HOT-TOPICS/sat_images.html">AVHRR images from DLR</a>
<li><a href="http://www.crseo.ucsb.edu/avhrr/avhrr.html">ICESS AVHRR Data Distribution, California</a>
<li><a href="http://skua.crseo.ucsb.edu/eosdis/">UCSB EOSDIS Prototype for AVHRR Data Processing</a>
<li><a href="http://www.tss.no/qlserv/">The Troms&#248; Satellite Station (TSS) NOAA AVHRR QL service</a>
<li><a href="http://www-db.cc.tohoku.ac.jp/jaidas/index-E.html">Japan Image Database (JAIDAS) at the Tohoku University</a>
<li><a href="http://graph.gsi-mc.go.jp:2000/www/Geographic/EODAS/EODAS_e.html">Earth Observation Data Analysis System, Japan</a>
<li><a href="http://opal-www.unh.edu/datasets/sst/sst.html">Gulf of Maine Sea Surface Temperature Data</a>
<li><a href="http://www.ccrs.emr.ca/linc/ps/digital/remote/cdavhrre.html">CCRS, CD-ROM AVHRR Canadian Images</a>
<li><a href="http://www.ccrs.emr.ca/linc/ps/digital/remote/davhrre.html">CCRS, AVHRR Data</a>
<li><a href="ftp://fermi.jhuapl.edu/www/seaspace/noaa.html">NOAA Imagery from the Space Oceanography Group, Johns Hopkins University, Applied Physics Laboratory</a>
<li><a href="http://www.orbimage.com/worbnet.htm">The OrbNet Active Archive will be introduced during the first half of 1996</a>
</ul>

