<h2>Other</h2>
<ul>
<LI><A HREF="gopher://newsserver.rrzn.uni-hannover.de:4320/1nntp">News, Hannover</A>
<LI><A HREF="http://www.rpi.edu/~decemj/index.html">John December Index Page</A>
