<LI><A HREF="gopher://gopher.sunet.se:70">SUNET info (Sweden)</A>
<li><A HREF="http://www.hal.com/%7Econnolly/html-test/service/validation-form.html">HaLsoft HTML Validation Service</A>
<BR>If your HTML is on a WWW server you can pass the HTTP URL to the <A
HREF="http://www.cc.gatech.edu/grads/j/Kipp.Jones/HaLidation/validation-form.html">Georgia
Tech</A> interface using the form below.
<FORM METHOD="POST" ACTION="http://www.cc.gatech.edu/cgi-bin/check-html.pl">
<INPUT NAME="HTML" SIZE="55" VALUE="http://"><BR>
<INPUT TYPE="submit" VALUE="Submit URL for validation">
<INPUT TYPE="reset" VALUE="Reset Form">
</FORM>
<li> <a href="http://ds.internic.net/ds/dspg1intdoc.html">InterNIC Internet Documentation (RFC's, FYI's, etc.)</a>
</UL>

