<H1>Suppliers of NOAA HRPT receiving equipment</H1>

Also check out the following lists
<ul>
<li><a href="http://seawifs.gsfc.nasa.gov/SEAWIFS/ANNOUNCEMENTS/930828_kirk_ground_stations">NASA SeaWifs, a list of suppliers of SeaWiFS-receiving equipment</a>

<li><a href="http://psbsgi1.nesdis.noaa.gov:8080/EBB/post/manulst.asc>
   A rather complete list covering the full spectrum of wxsat-related
   receiving equipment from NOAA/NESDIS</a>

<li><a href="mailto:wwinston@ssd.wwb.noaa.gov">Wayne Winston (NOAA/NESDIS)
maintains a world-wide list of receiving station manufacturers</a>

<li><a href="mailto:hinsman@www.wmo.ch">Dr. Don Hinsman<a> at the <a href="http://www.wmo.ch/">WMO</a> has a comprehensive worldwide list.
</ul>

