<html>
<HEAD><TITLE>Remote Sensing</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<pre><img src="logo/itc.gif" alt="ITC">                                  <img src="logo/sealwhb.gif" alt="WHB"></pre>
<hr>
<H1>Remote Sensing <img src="image/earthsmall.gif" alt=""></H1>
<br>
<i>
We can chop down all the trees,
<br>
poison all the rivers,
<br>
catch all the fish in the sea ...
<br>
In the end we will discover that we can't eat money.</i> -- Cree wisdom
<ul>
<li>Satellite Images and Data Sets, <a href="satellite.html">Organizations and Guides</a>
<li>Satellite Images and Data Sets, <a href="invdir.html">Inventory and Directory Services</a>.
<li><a href="gisearth.html">GIS and Earth</a>
<li><a href="ip.html">Image Processing and Pattern Recognition</a>
<li><a href="rstools.html">Remote Sensing related equipment</a>
<li><a href="airborne.html">Airborne Remote Sensing</a>
<p>
