<HEAD><TITLE>Image Processing and Pattern Recognition</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<pre><img src="logo/itc.gif" alt="ITC">                                  <img src="logo/sealwhb.gif" alt="WHB"></pre>
<hr>
<H1>Image Processing and Pattern Recognition</H1>

Also check out <a href="http://triton.cms.udel.edu/~oliver/oliver.html">Oliver Weatherbee's</a> <a href="http://triton.cms.udel.edu/~oliver/gis_gip/gis_gip_list.html">GIS and GIP Software Listing</a>!

<h2>Image Processing & GIS</h2>
<UL>
