  Pointers to many of these meteorological data sources
<A NAME=id261 HREF="http://walleye.forestry.umn.edu:70/0/www/rsgisinfo/rsgis.html">http://walleye.forestry.umn.edu:70/0/www/rsgisinfo/rsgis.html</A>
  Pointers to GIS and remote sensing sites
<A NAME=id262 HREF="http://www.atmos.uiuc.edu/">http://www.atmos.uiuc.edu/</A>
  A variety of resources for the atmospheric science community
<A NAME=id263 HREF="http://www.met.fu-berlin.de/DataSources/MetIndex.html">http://www.met.fu-berlin.de/DataSources/MetIndex.html</A>
  Pointers to many of these meteorological data sources 
<A NAME=id264 HREF="http://www.mth.uea.ac.uk/climateinfo.html">http://www.mth.uea.ac.uk/climateinfo.html</A>
  Pointers to oceanography, meteorological, general physical science resources
<A NAME=id265 HREF="http://zia.geog.buffalo.edu/GIAL/netgeog.html">http://zia.geog.buffalo.edu/GIAL/netgeog.html</A>
  Hypertext resource information, mostly for geography
</PRE>
