<HEAD>
<TITLE>AIHA Public Relations</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<BR>
<H1>AIHA Public Relations</H1>
AIHA's public relations team understands that achieving increased visibility for industrial
hygiene is based on much more than press releases and new slogans.
<P>
AIHA members are working on a daily basis to increase awareness of workplace safety for the
communities in which they work and live, and there are no better ambassadors than our members
to inform the public about the industrial hygiene profession.
<P>
AIHA has made a commitment to provide individual members with the tools to become directly
involved in promoting their profession.
<P>
<HR>
<H2>AIHA News</H2>
<A HREF="przack.html">S. Zack Mansdorf Assumes The Presidency of AIHA</A>
<P>
<A HREF="prboard.html"> AIHA Announces a New Board of Directors</A>
<P>
