<HR>
<IMG SRC="journal.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="[Journal Logo]">
<H2>The <I>AIHA Journal</I></H2>
Scientific and technical research on critical occupational and environmental health issues is
presented monthly in AIHA's flagship publication. Find out the most recent developments in
topics ranging from hazardous materials and indoor air quality to ergonomics and emergency
response.
<H3>Subscription Information</H3>
The <I>AIHA Journal</I> is free to most categories of membership. Nonmember
subscription prices are $120 domestic/$145 Canada and Mexico/$185 other foreign. Agent
discounts are available - please call for further information.
<P>
You may subscribe by credit card by calling (703) 849-8888 or send payment by mail to
AIHA Publication Orders, PO Box 27632, Richmond, VA 23261-7632.
<P>
<A HREF="./pubs/jrnlgdln.html"><I>American Industrial Hygiene Association Journal</I>
Guidelines for Authors</A>
<P>
<!--Add Later: AIHA Journal 10-Year Index-->
<P>
<HR>
<IMG SRC="graphics/synergis.gif" ALIGN=MIDDLE ALT="[Synergist Logo]">
<H2><I>The Synergist</I> Magazine</H2>
More than just a magazine reporting on association activities, <I>The Synergist</I> is a
vehicle for keeping current in the fields of health and safety.
<H3>Subscription Information</H3>
<I>The Synergist</I> is free to members. Nonmember subscription prices are $60
domestic/$85 foreign.<BR>
You may subscribe by credit card by calling (703) 849-8888 or send payment by mail to
AIHA Publication Orders, PO Box 27632, Richmond, VA 23261-7632.
<P>
