<HEAD>
<TITLE>AIHA Employment Services for Professionals</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<H1>AIHA Employment Services for Professionals</H1>
<BR>
Are you an industrial hygiene or occupational and environmental health and safety professional
looking for a new employment opportunity?
<P>
As content as you are with your present position, there may be a job out there that will persuade
you to make a change. The fact is, companies do make offers too good to refuse.
<P>
When you need a new job or you just want to see what is out there, review the services offered
by AIHA Employment Services and you'll know why many companies choose to use us when
looking for qualified professionals.  AIHA Employment Services is committed to connecting you
with the top companies looking for professionals in the occupational and environmental health
and safety industry.
<P>
Participating companies vary in size and type, and offer opportunities in all fields of occupational
and environmental health and safety.  There is no better way to secure that next employment
opportunity than with the AIHA Employment Services.
<P>
<H2>Employment Services and Benefits</H2>
<B>Professionals</B><BR>
<UL><LI>Three-month candidate registration: AIHA members - $30, Nonmembers - $100.
<P>
<LI>There is no middleman. You choose where and when to send your resume.
<P>
<LI>Access position openings via broadcast E-mail, InfoFax, or postal mail.
<P>
<LI>Interviewing opportunities are available at the AIHA annual conference, the <A
HREF="conf.html">American Industrial Hygiene Conference &amp; Exposition (AIHCE)</A>
in the spring.
<P>
</UL>
<P>
<H3>Call AIHA Employment Services to become part of our targeted candidate list.</H3>
<P>
<B>Employers</B><BR>
List your job position with AIHA! We have the finest selection of highly qualified candidates
available. Candidates are notified of your job description the same day we receive it. For
immediate results and response, go straight to the source for the professional industrial hygienist,
environmental, or a health and safety specialist.
<P>
<UL><LI>Compare our fees with any agency and major newspaper publication.
<P>
<LI>No lead in time - same day distribution.</UL></LI>
<P>
<B>Three-month (unlimited) listings plus a 10-line ad in The Synergist:</B><BR>
Organizational members: $450<BR>
Nonmember companies: $550<BR>
<P>
<B>Three-month (unlimited) listings:</B><BR>
Organizational members: $350<BR>
Nonmember companies: $450<BR>
<P>
<B>One-time mailing:</B><BR>
Organizational members: $250<BR>
Nonmember companies: $350<BR>
<P>
<H3>AIHA Employment Services boasts a high rate of successful hires and maintains an
outstanding record of participant satisfaction.</H3>

<P>
For more information, call AIHA Employment Services at (703)849-8888, or e-mail to <A
HREF="mailto:jwagner@aiha.org">jwagner@aiha.org</A><BR>
<P>
<A HREF="esmonth.html">Employment Monthly Service</A> |
<A HREF="index.html">Back to AIHA Home Page</A>
<BR>
</BODY>
