<H1><CENTER>Addendum C: Pro Forma Budget</CENTER></H1>
<HR>
<A HREF="#comparison">DUES COMPARISON</A><BR>
<A HREF="#costs">ONE-TIME COSTS</A> <BR>
<A HREF="#savings">EXPENSE SAVINGS BY NATURAL CLASSIFICATION</A><BR>
