Honorary Member; Master's Degree from University of Missouri; currently serves on Board of
Directors of the Cincinnati Society of Association Executives and has been active in the
American Society of Association Executives since 1971.


<H3>UTF FACILITATOR</H3>

<STRONG>Dadie Perlov</STRONG>, CAE, Founder and Principal, Consensus Management Group, with offices in New
